snippet.title: Ben 10 - Power of The Omnitrix - Full Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay of the awesome mobile Ben 10 game from the era of the original series - "Power of The Omnitrix"!

Official Website ➨ https://ben10club.org
Subscribe ➨ http://j.mp/Ben10ClubYouTube
Facebook ➨ https://www.facebook.com/ben10club.bg
Twitter ➨ https://twitter.com/ben10club_bg

Ben 10 Club is one of the world's biggest Ben 10 communities. It launched in 2010 as a small website and for 6 years it grew up to 2 million visits a month.
